description: [``botocore``] Update emr client to latest version

[``botocore``] This release introduces Standard Profile Objects, namely Asset and Case which contain values populated by data from third party systems and belong to a specific profile. This release adds an optional parameter, ObjectFilter to the ListProfileObjects API in order to search for these Standard Objects.
[``botocore``] This release adds ReplicationGroupCreateTime field to ReplicationGroup which indicates the UTC time when ElastiCache ReplicationGroup is created
